"},{"pid":"557509d20cc3bcdbc0da3a50af78de6b7baa799b","tid":2244190,"uid":26014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T10:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8038497c24aba78b5cbbbd4feec1543d3bc7dc4d","tid":2244190,"uid":19126,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T10:17:00.000Z","msg":"我想講口供就咁睇可能係唔可靠既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早上出門後流連到晚上，目睹拆欄縱火等行為後仍然逗留，因為被告可生事破壞，並無意圖回家<br />\n<br />\n但你點得出呢個結論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先冇證人，然後就係見到有破壞仲逗留咁又點？你藍絲拆連儂牆班狗都睇住啦，咁又點呀？<br />\n<br />\n第二，十幾歲仔一早出門流連到晚上不知幾正常啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你個閪官不如話你點都判佢有罪仲直接啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n帶衫又意圖犯罪帶泳鏡又意圖犯罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3aa80955604865182c5905893bd2091ee497bc","tid":2244190,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T10:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f3dde8991d4076138549924fb5af2e1744bc64","tid":2244190,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T10:25:58.000Z","msg":"日日出嚟尻判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47880c88c969f20b940b03f6320f0ef52187f0ce","tid":2244190,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T10:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\